From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 15 Mar 2026 19:07:39 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: add semantic corpus analysis command (dockg
 semantic-analyze)

New dockg_semantic_analysis.py:
- LanguageMeasures: total/unique words, TTR, avg sentence/chunk length,
  lexical density, Flesch-Kincaid grade level
- Cross-document theme analysis (human-readable topics by doc spread)
- Named entity analysis (core concepts spanning most documents)
- Global keyword profile (stopword-filtered content words)
- Section heading vocabulary (structural outline of corpus)
- Per-document vocabulary signatures (top keywords + entities per doc)
- Corpus cohesion score (% of themes spanning >=3 documents)
- Strengths/issues insights from all measures
- Markdown + JSON output; mirrors DocKGAnalyzer pattern

New CLI command: dockg semantic-analyze
  --repo, --db, --lancedb, --output, --json, --quiet

